  "text": "The β1Int-HaloTag fusion protein was transfected into mammalian cell lines using the cell-specific lipofection reagents from Mirus, according to manufacturer protocols. Co-transfection experiments using β1Int-HaloTag and humanized renilla luciferase or monster GFP (Promega) were done at a 1:1 ratio. Cells stably expressing β1Int-HaloTag or HaloTag-(NLS) [CITATION_1] were generated using a 3:1 ratio of β1Int-HaloTag or HaloTag-(NLS) [CITATION_2] and pcINeo (Promega).",
